title: Fantastic Voyage (1966) Raquel Welch STEREO (Opt.SWESUBS)
description:
Optional Swedish subs in separate idx/sub files. <a href="

Classic Sci-Fi about the submarine with a small crew shrunken to microscopic size and injected into the bloodstream of a scientist to save his life. Surprising stereo sound and widescreen.

I had no idea that this film still was so popular. A recent upload of the full DVD gathered hundreds of downloaders, so I made this rip for those of you who cannot handle such dinosaurs. Thanks to Wormman for the upload.

DVDrip XviD 2-pass.
Widescreen 704x368, stereo AC3.

Burn tested, runs well in both my standalone DivX player.
